src:
Hasil FP3 MotoGP Malaysia: Franco Morbidelli-Fabio Quartararo Tercepat
02 Nov 2019, 10:50 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Petronas Yamaha SRT, Franco Morbidelli, sukses mencatat waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas ketiga (FP3) MotoGP Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Sabtu (2/11/2019).
Pebalap Prancis ini diikuti oleh tandemnya sendiri, Fabio Quartararo, di posisi kedua dan pebalap Repsol Honda, Marc Marquez, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap Monster Energy Yamaha, Maverick Vinales, dan pebalap Pramac Racing, Jack Miller.
Berikut hasil FP3 MotoGP Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian MotoGP FP3 Results: Fastest Franco Morbidelli-Fabio Quartararo
02 Nov 2019, 10:50 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Yamaha SRT Petronas rider, Franco Morbidelli, successfully recorded the fastest time in the third free practice session (FP3) of the Malaysian MotoGP at Sepang Circuit on Saturday (11/02/2019).
The Frenchman was followed by his own tandem, Fabio Quartararo, in second place and Repsol Honda rider Marc Marquez, in third position.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by Monster Energy Yamaha racer, Maverick Vinales, and Pramac Racing driver Jack Miller.
Following are the results of the 2013 MotoGP Malaysia Malaysian FP3.
